data.title: Ponette, Another Nordic Musical Star To Add To An Already Shining Galaxy
data.meta_description: Ponette have just released their debut EP, 'I'm Alone', a dark slice of electronica served with ice-cold vocals and a wedge of bittersweet lyrics on the side.
